Prominent political analyst Prince Mashele, who has been critical of the ANC and its administration in recent weeks, had allegedly applied to be a public representative of the DA before the recent elections. In his column in Sowetan newspaper, Mashele launched a blistering attack on President Cyril Ramaphosa and labelled his cabinet ministers Angie Motshekga and Blade Nzimande as"expired dinosaurs" and "fossils". TO READ MORE ON THIS STORY GET A COPY OF TODAY'S SUNDAY WORLD